# 🛠️ North Region - Asset & Tools Inventory Dashboard

This repository contains the interactive Asset Management and Tools Tracking system for the **North Region Team**. 

## 🚀 Live Dashboard
You can access the live tracking system here:
👉 **[https://shakirsir59.github.io/North-Tools-Inventory/](https://shakirsir59.github.io/North-Tools-Inventory/)**

---

## ✨ Key Features
* **Live Inventory Analytics:** Dynamic Bar and Donut charts showing real-time distribution of laptops, SIM cards, and mobile devices.
* **Granular Tracking:** Every asset is mapped with its specific Serial Number, IMEI, or Mobile Number based on actual records.
* **Auto-Duplicate Detector:** Built-in conflict engine that automatically flags an alert if a unique asset (SIM/Serial) is mistakenly assigned to multiple users.
* **Interactive Admin Controls:** Easily Add, Edit, or Delete team members and tool shuffles directly from the UI without changing the backend code.

