## 🛠️ Technology Stack
* **Frontend:** HTML5, Tailwind CSS (for modern UI styling)
* **Charts Engine:** Chart.js (for real-time data visualization)
* **Data Storage:** Browser LocalStorage (retains changes locally upon layout updates)
